16#ifndef RDATA_GENERIC_CDNSKEY_60_C
17#define RDATA_GENERIC_CDNSKEY_60_C
18
19#include <dst/dst.h>
20
21#define RRTYPE_CDNSKEY_ATTRIBUTES 0
22
23static inline isc_result_t
24fromtext_cdnskey(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
25
26 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_cdnskey);
27
28 return (generic_fromtext_key(rdclass, type, lexer, origin,
29 options, target, callbacks));
30}
31
32static inline isc_result_t
33totext_cdnskey(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
34
35 REQUIRE(rdata != NULL);
36 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_cdnskey);
37
38 return (generic_totext_key(rdata, tctx, target));
39}
40
41static inline isc_result_t
42fromwire_cdnskey(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
43
44 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_cdnskey);
45
46 return (generic_fromwire_key(rdclass, type, source, dctx,
47 options, target));
48}
49
50static inline isc_result_t
51towire_cdnskey(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
52 isc_region_t sr;
53
54 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_cdnskey);
55 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
56
57 UNUSED(cctx);
58
59 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
60 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
61}
62
63static inline int
64compare_cdnskey(ARGS_COMPARE) {
65 isc_region_t r1;
66 isc_region_t r2;
67
68 REQUIRE(rdata1 != NULL);
69 REQUIRE(rdata2 != NULL);
70 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
71 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
72 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_cdnskey);
73 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
74 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
75
76 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
77 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
78 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
79}
80
81static inline isc_result_t
82fromstruct_cdnskey(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
83
84 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_cdnskey);
85
86 return (generic_fromstruct_key(rdclass, type, source, target));
87}
88
89static inline isc_result_t
90tostruct_cdnskey(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
91 dns_rdata_cdnskey_t *dnskey = target;
92
93 REQUIRE(dnskey != NULL);
94 REQUIRE(rdata != NULL);
95 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_cdnskey);
96
97 dnskey->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
98 dnskey->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
99 ISC_LINK_INIT(&dnskey->common, link);
100
101 return (generic_tostruct_key(rdata, target, mctx));
102}
103
104static inline void
105freestruct_cdnskey(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
106 dns_rdata_cdnskey_t *dnskey = (dns_rdata_cdnskey_t *) source;
107
108 REQUIRE(dnskey != NULL);
109 REQUIRE(dnskey->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_cdnskey);
110
111 generic_freestruct_key(source);
112}
113
114static inline isc_result_t
115additionaldata_cdnskey(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
116 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_cdnskey);
117
118 UNUSED(rdata);
119 UNUSED(add);
120 UNUSED(arg);
121
122 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
123}
124
125static inline isc_result_t
126digest_cdnskey(ARGS_DIGEST) {
127 isc_region_t r;
128
129 REQUIRE(rdata != NULL);
130 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_cdnskey);
131
132 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
133
134 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
135}
136
137static inline bool
138checkowner_cdnskey(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
139
140 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_cdnskey);
141
142 UNUSED(name);
143 UNUSED(type);
144 UNUSED(rdclass);
145 UNUSED(wildcard);
146
147 return (true);
148}
149
150static inline bool
151checknames_cdnskey(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
152
153 REQUIRE(rdata != NULL);
154 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_cdnskey);
155
156 UNUSED(rdata);
157 UNUSED(owner);
158 UNUSED(bad);
159
160 return (true);
161}
162
163static inline int
164casecompare_cdnskey(ARGS_COMPARE) {
165
166 /*
167 * Treat ALG 253 (private DNS) subtype name case sensistively.
168 */
169 return (compare_cdnskey(rdata1, rdata2));
170}

172#endif /* RDATA_GENERIC_CDNSKEY_60_C */
